channel.title: Bootstrapped.fm episode 104 "I Don’t Want To Talk About GDPR The Whole Time w/ Natalie Nagele from Wildbit"
channel.description:
In this episode we’re joined by [Natalie Nagele](https://twitter.com/natalienagele) from [Wildbit](http://wildbit.com) to talk about starting a business vs. consulting, employees with side hustles, how to pick conferences to attend, and yes, GDPR.
**[Listen to the episode here.](http://bootstrapped.fm/2018/05/31/104-i-dont-want-to-talk-about-gdpr-the-whole-time-w-natalie-nagele-from-wildbit/)**
